*Pitanja* su zanimljiva i korisna za razumevanje. (Questions are interesting and useful for understanding.)

Postoje razna *pitanja* koja se postavljaju. (There are various questions that are asked.)

Postoje mnoga *pitanje* o ovom procesu. (There are many questions about this process.)

Kako bi se steklo bolje razumevanje, postavljaju se neka *pitanja*. (In order to gain better understanding, some questions are asked.)

Mnoga *pitanja* ostaju neodgovorena. (Many questions remain unanswered.)